text: Frederick Nnaemeka Leonard (born may 1,1980) is a Nigerian actor. He won the award for Best Supporting Actor at the Golden Icons Academy Movie Awards in 2014. He also won Best Actor at the Zulu African Film Academy Awards in 2016. ==Awards and nominations== Year Award Category Work Result Ref 2014 Golden Icons Academy Movie Awards Best Supporting Actor 2015 Golden Icons Academy Movie Awards Best Actor 2016 City People Movie Award Best Supporting Actor of the Year (English) Zulu African Film Academy Awards Best Actor Woeman == References == Category:1980 births Category:Living people Category:Nigerian actors
